{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6966429\charrsid15878306 talking}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1770950\charrsid15878306  before, I - we - we made our presents. Yes.
