\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13047860 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1770950\charrsid15878306 How did you get on with the other people that you were working with?
